CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 15, 1941, pg. 22, reads: "At 21st Birthday Celebration - Friends and relatives of Theodore (Pete) Mabrey Jr., 1369 Valley Rue Street, Pittsburgh, surprised him last week with a birthday party marking his 21st milestone. He is the son of Mr. and Mrs. Theodore R. Mabrey Sr. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of men, possibly including Theodore "Pete" Mabrey Jr. wearing moustache and three piece tweed suit, and women, including one wearing dark dress with light colored bow, posed on floor behind coffee table with cake with six candles, for Mabrey's twenty-first birthday party in domestic interior with lace curtains and floral rug
